{
  "stem": "25773.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he said I'll help you with the new papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was like a fortune, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I couldn't dream about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But because he worked for the underground, he could manage the finances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was a source of-- because I was sent after the war-- it was called [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Felicia. ?] It was an organization that helped Jews and Christians, mostly Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Probably got the money from America or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he said, I meet you here in two weeks' time, on the same route, on the same place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so we met in two weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Every two weeks I met him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he said your papers are being made.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was difficult because what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They have to find a birth certificate of a dead person to be authentic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the dead person had to be approximately of my age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there were a lot of priests included in this plot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And there were the government-- the government in hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Not the government.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The organization, the actual organization in hiding, helped a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the movement, the resistance movement in Poland, was really very prominent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I mean, they speak of French marquees and things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But the Polish underground was fierce, and dedicated, and widespread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Anyway, meanwhile, one day-- I already had a little money, and my cousin gave me straight away an address to his friend, who was a safe person.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "That I could lodge there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I don't need to sleep on the stairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I was sleeping on the stairs for weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And then at Roman's place at the garage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So I told Roman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I thanked him very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I went to this place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "She was a beautiful woman, had a house.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
